YOUR PANEL (controls available to you):
- Main Bus tie switches: A, B, C, D (open / position 1 / position 2)
- Fuel Cell reactant valves: 1, 2, 3, 4 (open / close; minimum / nominal / maximum)
- Battery charger breakers: 1, 2, 3, 4 (in / out / reset; charge rate minimum / nominal / maximum)
- Inverters: 1, 2, 3, 4, standby (online / offline; load minimum / nominal / maximum)
- AC load centers: 1, 2, 3, 4 (shed / restore at minimum / nominal / maximum)
- Cabin vent valves: A, B, C, D (open / close); repress valve (minimum / nominal / maximum)
- Life-support loops: 1, 2, 3, 4 (isolate / restore); CO2 scrubbers: 1, 2, 3, 4 (fan minimum / nominal / maximum)
- Coolant loops: 1, 2, 3, 4 (primary or backup pump; radiator bypass minimum / nominal / maximum)
- Cryo tank heaters: 1, 2, 3, 4 (minimum / nominal / maximum); manifold isolation valves A, B, C, D
- RCS quad isolation valves: 1, 2, 3, 4; manifolds A, B, C, D (pressure minimum / nominal / maximum); regulators 1, 2, 3, 4
- IMU select: 1, 2, 3, 4; attitude control modes A, B, C, D (align rate minimum / nominal / maximum)
- Circuit breakers for every subsystem (in / out / reset)
